Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Bolo Norte Elementary School in Barangay Bolo Norte in the Municipality of Sipocot, Province of Camarines Sur, to Soledad R. Villafuerte Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 850
An Act Changing the Name of the Bolo Norte Elementary School in Barangay Bolo Norte in the Municipality of Sipocot, Province of Camarines Sur, to Soledad R. Villafuerte Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Bolo Norte Elementary School in Barangay Bolo Norte in the Municipality of Sipocot, Province of Camarines Sur, is hereby changed to Soledad R. Villafuerte Elementary School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
